divs: Sighting Detailscame out of the explorer after hiking with my girlfriend and dog. looked up at the sky and noticed this bright object in the west traveling towards us. it was much bright than all the stars. i would say as bright as jupiter. it had no blinking airplane lights and was completly silent. to bright to be a sattelite also it slightly changed directions so i feel it rules out satelite.
